Acer Records Rapid Sales Growth in China, FT Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-05-20T00:49:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/acer-records-rapid-sales-growth-in-china-ft-reports-correct-.html
(Corrects company name.)  Acer Inc. is registering accelerated
sales growth in  China , the Financial Times reported, citing an
interview with Oliver Ahrens, president of Acer China. The
company expects its full-year revenue in the country to soar by
70 percent from 2010 sales, to about $2.5 billion, Ahrens said,
according to the FT.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  